mosh on FreeBSD
===============

1. Install
----------

- Install following ports:
  devel/gmake
  devel/oniguruma5
  math/gmp
- ./configure CFLAGS=-I/usr/local/include LDFLAGS=-L/usr/local/lib
- gmake

2. Limitations
--------------

- mosh is currently only tested at i386 and amd64 architecture.
- mosh needs procfs. This will be fixed in future release.

